  <brief_title>A Phase III Study of Brimonidine Tartrate Ophthalmic Solution, 0.15% in Patients With Open-Angle Glaucoma or Ocular Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Study of Brimonidine Tartrate Ophthalmic Solution, 0.15% in Patients With Open-Angle Glaucoma or Ocular Hypertension</official_title>
